creator: Global Initiative Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Inkpath is the first all-round study performance app, designed for university students, researchers and staff who want to maximise additional development opportunities to drive lifelong career growth.

It helps you navigate what can be a dizzying array of potential avenues to take during your time at your university and track your skills development, which can then be used to progress your studies and career.

With Inkpath you can:
• Analyse your current strengths and weaknesses and select what skills you need to improve in order to be better prepared for your future career and ambitions. 
• Explore all the activities and extra-curricular training opportunities offered by the university, and get recommendations on the ones that will help you develop the skills you really need. 
• Log your time and add your own reflections on every activity you complete, which will count towards your overall goals. 
• Use this information to apply for jobs or further academic opportunities, to showcase fully what you have achieved, your skills and your learning.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: User experience improvements including a popup reminder to complete activities.
